<p>Katak-support installer requires ability to write to the configuration file, <strong>include/ktk-config.php</strong>. A template copy is located in the <i>include</i> directory (<strong><i>include/ktk-config-sample.php</i></strong>).</p>
<p><strong>Rename</strong> the sample file to <strong>ktk-config.php</strong> and click install below.</p>
<p>If the sample config file is missing - please make sure you uploaded all files or refer to the <a href="http://katak-support.com/node/6" target="_blank">Installation Guide.</a></p>
